            <p>
                Our project explores the relationship between seasonal changes and the popularity of various music
                genres on Spotify. Music consumption is deeply personal and culturally significant, influenced by factors
                like mood, weather, and social activities tied to seasonal shifts. By understanding how genres perform
                throughout the year, we aim to uncover consumer behavior insights that could lead to tailored marketing
                strategies, personalized playlists, and deeper user engagement.
